    howToGetThere: "Enter the park at the Monjo checkpost \u2014 reached by trekking 2 days from Lukla airport via Phakding. Fly to Lukla from Kathmandu (35 min) to access the park's main entry point. Helicopter charters from Kathmandu to Namche Bazaar or higher destinations within the park are also available.",
