    howToGetThere: "Kala Patthar is reached by trekking to Gorakshep (5,164 m) \u2014 approximately 12\u201314 days from Lukla via the classic EBC route through Namche, Tengboche, Dingboche, and Lobuche. From Gorakshep, the ascent to Kala Patthar summit takes 1.5\u20132 hours on a steep but non-technical trail.",
